\newlabel{fig:pareto}{{4}{5}{Compression ratio vs.\ cosine similarity Pareto frontier. Each point represents a compression method. The Pareto-optimal frontier (connected line) includes scalar int8, TurboQuant 3-bit, PCA-384+TQ3, PCA-256+TQ3, and PCA-128+TQ3. Binary quantization and product quantization fall below the frontier}{figure.4}{}}
